w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/corey-taylor-dave-grohl@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/corey-taylor-dave-grohl@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/corey-taylor-dave-grohl@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/corey-taylor-dave-grohl@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slipknot">活结乐队</a>主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/corey-taylor">科里·泰勒</a>透露，他认为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dave-grohl">戴夫·格罗尔</a>在婚外生孩子是“不负责任的”，但“并不意味着他不是一个好人”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/foo-fighters-live-in-manchester-setlist-photos-3765719">喷火战机生活在曼彻斯特：所向披靡，仍然不可撼动</a></strong></li></ul><p>本月早些时候，这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Foo-Fighters">喷火战机</a>歌手透露， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dave-grohl-shares-that-hes-become-a-father-outside-of-my-marriage-3792457">他已成为一名婚外女婴的父亲</a>，但他正在“尽一切努力重新赢得妻子乔丁·布鲁姆和家人的信任”。他和布鲁姆已经有了三个女儿：维奥莱特、哈珀和奥菲莉亚。</p><p>随后，一篇帖子疯传，声称新生女婴被命名为 Roxie Junie Grohl，并且她“真正是一个彻头彻尾的 Grohl”。该帖子被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dave-grohls-representatives-debunk-viral-love-child-post-circulating-on-social-media-3793929">揭穿为虚假信息，格罗尔的代表向<em>NME</em>证实了这一点</a>。</p><p>现在，格罗尔的老朋友科里·泰勒 (Corey Taylor) 对这一情况发表了评论，这<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/foo-fighters-pull-out-of-soundside-music-festival-with-jack-white-replacing-the-band-3797478">导致喷火战机取消了上周末在 Soundside 音乐节的演出</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3784460" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3784460" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3784460" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Dave-Grohl-CREDIT-Photo-by-Helle-Arensbak-_-Ritzau-Scanpix-_-AFP-_-Denmark-OUT-Photo-by-HELLE-ARENSBAK_Ritzau-Scanpix_AFP-via-Getty-Images.jpg" alt="喷火战机主唱戴夫·格罗尔" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Dave-Grohl-CREDIT-Photo-by-Helle-Arensbak-_-Ritzau-Scanpix-_-AFP-_-Denmark-OUT-Photo-by-HELLE-ARENSBAK_Ritzau-Scanpix_AFP-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Dave-Grohl-CREDIT-Photo-by-Helle-Arensbak-_-Ritzau-Scanpix-_-AFP-_-Denmark-OUT-Photo-by-HELLE-ARENSBAK_Ritzau-Scanpix_AFP-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Dave-Grohl-CREDIT-Photo-by-Helle-Arensbak-_-Ritzau-Scanpix-_-AFP-_-Denmark-OUT-Photo-by-HELLE-ARENSBAK_Ritzau-Scanpix_AFP-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Dave-Grohl-CREDIT-Photo-by-Helle-Arensbak-_-Ritzau-Scanpix-_-AFP-_-Denmark-OUT-Photo-by-HELLE-ARENSBAK_Ritzau-Scanpix_AFP-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Dave-Grohl-CREDIT-Photo-by-Helle-Arensbak-_-Ritzau-Scanpix-_-AFP-_-Denmark-OUT-Photo-by-HELLE-ARENSBAK_Ritzau-Scanpix_AFP-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Dave-Grohl-CREDIT-Photo-by-Helle-Arensbak-_-Ritzau-Scanpix-_-AFP-_-Denmark-OUT-Photo-by-HELLE-ARENSBAK_Ritzau-Scanpix_AFP-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3784460" class="wp-caption-text">喷火战机主唱 Dave Grohl – 图片来源：Helle Arensbak/Ritzau Scanpix/AFP via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>泰勒出现在由喜剧演员汤姆·塞古拉和克里斯蒂娜·帕西茨基主持的“<em>你妈妈之家</em>”播客的最新一期节目中，他被要求分享他对“混乱”情况的看法。他首先解释说，他认为格罗尔宣布出生是为了“抢先”婴儿的母亲亲自宣布这一消息。</p><p>他继续说道：“显然，这是非常不负责任的。我知道有很多粉丝因为他塑造的形象而感到失望。但我必须提醒人们，我们并不完美。他是最后一批真正拥有这种形象的人之一……”</p><p> “发生这种情况并不意味着他不是一个好人，因为我碰巧认识他这个人。这意味着他有他妈的问题，而且他搞砸了。他并不完美。对于他的家人来说，这将是非常困难的。我不会对它发生的原因或方式做出任何假设。我很清醒，但与此同时，我也经历了自己的痛苦。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="克里斯汀回来了+科里·泰勒谈论戴夫·格罗尔和简的成瘾戏剧| YMH Ep。第778章" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/gsHtBGXUV2U?start=5969&enable